Description

		Mask 4 wood print by John Anderson.   Bring your artwork to life with the texture and added depth of a wood print.   Your image gets printed directly onto a sheet of 3/4" thick maple wood.  There are D-clips on the back of the print for mounting it to your wall using mounting hooks and nails (included).	



Ships Within

			2 - 3 business days		


Ships From

			Atlanta, GA		










